original_title: Rabbit Ears - Brer Rabbit and the Wonderful Tar Baby
overview: When Brer Fox gets tired of Brer Rabbit's sassiness, he decides to make a Tar Baby that will trap Brer Rabbit for sure. But Brer Fox soon finds out that Brer Rabbit is trickier than he looks.
title: Rabbit Ears - Brer Rabbit and the Wonderful Tar Baby
